----------
2002/06/04 11:03:34 crs
base/CLog.cpp

fixed delete bug in printt -- when skipping file and line the
deleted pointer was wrong.

----------
2002/06/04 11:02:33 crs
synergy/CXWindowsClipboard.cpp

